c: 2
v: 17
t: "hal almunafiqin aladhin amanuu -zahrana la batnana- brsalt muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, thuma kfru, fsaru ytkhbtwn fi zlmat dlalhm wahum la ysherwn, wala 'amal lahum fi alkhuruj mnha, tushbh hal jamaeat fi laylat mzlmt, wawqd 'ahaduhum narana ezymt lldf' wal'ida't, falamaa stet alnaar wanart ma hwlh, antfat waetmt, fsar 'ashabaha fi zulumat laa yarawn shyyana, wala yahtadun 'iilaa tariq wala mkhrj"